WEBVTT

00:07:26.442 --> 00:07:33.442
So it’s natural that young girls consider
you their inspiration, their idol.

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:38.279
Please tell them some things
to keep in mind,

00:07:38.280 --> 00:07:40.959
some thought you have
which will help them move ahead.

00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:47.559
EK: The biggest thing is to pursue your
passion. A lot of people have said this.

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:50.227
But for a girl, it is very tough
to pursue one’s passion,

00:07:50.400 --> 00:07:54.520
because you have to fit into different
roles while pursuing your passion.

00:07:55.640 --> 00:08:00.530
To make your choice secondary has become
like second nature to you.